messages.content: what is the annual revenue for 2024?

who is the ceo and what is her background?

The CEO is Sarah Johnson. Her background includes:

* Former VP of Engineering at Google Cloud (8 years)
* MBA from Stanford GSB
* BS Computer Science from MIT
* Led Google Cloud ML platform to $2B revenue
* Recognition as Forbes 30 Under 30 (2018) and Fortune 40 Under 40 (2023).
